          <text><![CDATA[<p>Urges the people of the United States to recognize the 40th anniversary of the passage of the Solar Energy Research, Development, and Demonstration Act of 1974.</p> <p>Recognizes the National Renewable Energy Laboratory's research and work to improve renewable energy and energy efficiency technologies.</p> <p>Expresses the sense of the House of Representatives that the United States should make a commitment to provide adequate funding to support the Laboratory.</p> <ul> </ul>]]></text>
